Package: multiRF
Type: Package
Title: MRF-Based Multi-Omics Integration and Clustering
Version: 0.2.1
Author: Wei Zhang
Maintainer: Wei Zhang <wzhang0739@gmail.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("Wei", "Zhang", email = "wzhang0739@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Integrates matched multi-omics datasets using multivariate
    random forests with inverse minimal depth (IMD) importance. Provides
    workflows for model fitting, variable selection, clustering, and
    visualization.
